Virtuix Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg










































  





















































































July 29, 2017 12:42 AM ET
Software

Company Overview of Virtuix Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Virtuix Inc. provides an active virtual reality motion platform for gaming applications. It offers Virtuix Omni, a motion platform that enables 360-degree mobility in virtual environments. The company’s Virtuix Omni includes Omni shoes that allow extended, fast-paced gameplay sessions; Virtuix Omni tracking pods that attach to the Omni shoes and track the movement of each foot at all times; Omni Harness that provides safety and versatility for rapid 360-degree turns, jumps, and unconstrained movements; and Virtuix VR boom, a standalone accessory that manages HMD cable during virtual reality experience. The company sells its products online. The company was incorporated in 2013 and is based i...
Virtuix Inc. provides an active virtual reality motion platform for gaming applications. It offers Virtuix Omni, a motion platform that enables 360-degree mobility in virtual environments. The company’s Virtuix Omni includes Omni shoes that allow extended, fast-paced gameplay sessions; Virtuix Omni tracking pods that attach to the Omni shoes and track the movement of each foot at all times; Omni Harness that provides safety and versatility for rapid 360-degree turns, jumps, and unconstrained movements; and Virtuix VR boom, a standalone accessory that manages HMD cable during virtual reality experience. The company sells its products online. The company was incorporated in 2013 and is based in Austin, Texas. Virtuix Inc. operates as a subsidiary of Virtuix Holdings Inc.
Detailed Description


Austin, TX United StatesFounded in 2013



www.virtuix.com







